snippet.title: Search for a Dark Matter annihilation signal from the Galactic Center halo with H.E.S.S
snippet.description: Search for a Dark Matter annihilation signal from the Galactic Center halo with H.E.S.S / . E. S. S. collaboration A search for a very-high-energy (VHE; >= 100 GeV) gamma-ray signal from self-annihilating particle Dark Matter (DM) is performed towards a region of projected distance r ~ 45-150 pc from the Galactic Center.
